# 🚀 ORIAN -multi-agent autonomy that ships real work, end-to-end.

> **"From a single objective to fully executed, production-ready output — autonomously."**

[![Node.js](https://img.shields.io/badge/Backend-Node.js%20%2F%20Express-339933?style=flat-square&logo=node.js)](https://nodejs.org)
[![React](https://img.shields.io/badge/Frontend-React%2018-61DAFB?style=flat-square&logo=react)](https://react.dev)
[![PostgreSQL](https://img.shields.io/badge/State%20Ledger-PostgreSQL-4169E1?style=flat-square&logo=postgresql)](https://postgresql.org)
[![Redis](https://img.shields.io/badge/Queue-Upstash%20Redis%20%2F%20BullMQ-DC382D?style=flat-square&logo=redis)](https://upstash.com)
[![Groq](https://img.shields.io/badge/LLM-Groq%20llama--3.1--8b--instant-F55036?style=flat-square)](https://groq.com)
[![Tavily](https://img.shields.io/badge/Web%20Search-Tavily%20API-0EA5E9?style=flat-square)](https://tavily.com)
[![Socket.io](https://img.shields.io/badge/Streaming-Socket.io-010101?style=flat-square&logo=socket.io)](https://socket.io)
