## 🗂️ Repository Structure

```
Orian/
├── backend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── agents/          # Decomposition, Research, Architecture, CodeGen agents
│   │   ├── queue/           # BullMQ worker and job processor
│   │   ├── db/              # PostgreSQL client, migrations, schema
│   │   ├── routes/          # Express REST endpoints
│   │   ├── socket/          # Socket.io event emitters
│   │   └── index.js         # Server entrypoint
│   ├── .env.example         # Environment variable template
│   └── package.json
├── frontend/
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/      # GoalInput, AgentStream, OutputPanel
│   │   ├── hooks/           # useSocket, useTaskState
│   │   └── App.jsx          # Root component
│   └── package.json
└── README.md
```

