## 🧰 Full Technology Stack

| Layer | Technology | Role |
|---|---|---|
| **Frontend** | React 18 | Interactive dashboard UI |
| **Backend** | Node.js / Express | REST API and Socket.io server |
| **State Ledger** | PostgreSQL | ACID-compliant sub-task persistence |
| **Async Queue** | Upstash Cloud Redis + BullMQ | Durable job queuing and worker dispatch |
| **LLM Reasoning** | Groq — `llama-3.1-8b-instant` | Ultra-low-latency multi-step inference |
| **Live Web Search** | Tavily Search API | Real-time evidence grounding |
| **Streaming** | Socket.io | Bidirectional real-time event delivery |
| **Queue Protocol** | `rediss://` (TLS) | Encrypted Upstash Redis connection |

